{"tid":519089,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支持香港警察由連登仔做起","createTime":"2018-01-04T04:10:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-04T13:28:17.000Z","uid":7369,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ade73b74937a0420814319e25993cf0958f5cb99","tid":519089,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T04:10:28.000Z","msg":"鑒於近日接連有警員因不同原因被法庭判罪而喪失本身應有福利, 而現任警務處長盧偉聰亦表示將來會對犯罪警員及其家人給予最好的協助及支持。在此小弟呼籲香港廣大市民響網上聯署, 要求警務處長盧偉聰對所有犯罪而被判刑嘅警員一視同仁, 對所有犯罪警員及其家人給予最好的協助及支持!<br />\n<br />\n我懇請連登巴打幫手例出近年所有犯罪警員資料, 希望可以俾到壓力警務處長對有關警員作出支援同協助! <br />\n<br />\n<ins>警員姓名 - 干犯罪行</ins><br />\n朱經緯 - 襲擊致造成身體傷害罪<br />\n潘俊東 (疑犯) - 涉藏有少量毒品氯氨酮<br />\n李偉嘉 (疑犯) - 被控強姦罪<br />\n<br />\n請幫手加入罪件以及相關警員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a62832c4b6178e37bce5066af1fc4e5cdbc27ba0","tid":519089,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T04:11:57.000Z","msg":"集齊case之後再請有相關知識嘅巴打放上網聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b1a7e7bc0397d645f33752abffda4c50cc23348","tid":519089,"uid":7369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T04:26:46.000Z","msg":"孫梓聰 - 遊蕩導致他人擔心罪"},{"pid":"d925a1ced794a8f4de43f712b526658178c18899","tid":519089,"uid":7369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T04:32:03.000Z","msg":"袁樂欣 - 普通襲擊罪成"},{"pid":"fd6d2039de37cd4691b4451c10a11d8d5e711792","tid":519089,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T04:54:36.000Z","msg":"處長：我講㗎咋喎！"},{"pid":"6ddc3a85a3f3ce4d4d75c8e73b9f29b2a0b0b501","tid":519089,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T04:56:35.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/